= Rad Seo

RadSeo provides fine tune SEO tweaking tools for Radiant CMS.

= Features

 * Sitemap.xml & Robots.txt Tools
   * Update Frequency, Priority & Indexed? fields in page meta data.
   * Valid Sitemap.xml generated using above fields.
   * robots.txt file generated denying access to all pages where index for search? is set to false.
 * Additional Radius Tags
   * SEO Title Tag and Link Title Attribute fields added to page meta data. 
   * <r:page_title /> will display a <title></title> tag containing either A) the text in the SEO Title Tag field, or B) the default radiant page name.
   * <r:link /> will add a title attribute to your link (<a>) when linking to a page with text in the Link Title Attribute field.


